text: Amirul Islam is an Indian politician belonging to All India Trinamool Congress. In 2016 he was elected as MLA of Samserganj Vidhan Sabha Constituency in West Bengal Legislative Assembly.List of Winners in West Bengal 2016 ==References== Category:Living people Category:All India Trinamool Congress politicians Category:West Bengal MLAs 2016– Category:Year of birth missing (living people)
